        <h4 class="subsection-header">📅 AI Chat System: NEXT STEPS (Daily/Weekly Milestones for Developers)</h4>
        
        <div class="plan-detail">
            <h5>🔴 THIS WEEK (Days 1-5): Phase 1 Completion - Database Model Classes</h5>
            <div style="background: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0; border-radius: 5px;">
                <p><strong>Daily Objectives:</strong></p>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Day 1:</strong> Verify database schema initialization works
                        <ul>
                            <li>Start app, check application logs for: "ai_chat_schema - AI Chat schema check complete"</li>
                            <li>Verify no critical errors in startup logs (warnings about table creation are expected/normal)</li>
                            <li>Reference: <code>Comserv.pm:_initialize_ai_chat_schema()</code> lines 303-342</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Day 2:</strong> Create DBIx::Class Result classes for 5 tables
                        <ul>
                            <li>Create: <code>lib/Comserv/Model/Schema/Ency/Result/DocumentationMetadataIndex.pm</code></li>
                            <li>Create: <code>lib/Comserv/Model/Schema/Ency/Result/CodeSearchIndex.pm</code></li>
                            <li>Create: <code>lib/Comserv/Model/Schema/Ency/Result/WebSearchResults.pm</code></li>
                            <li>Create: <code>lib/Comserv/Model/Schema/Ency/Result/AiModelConfig.pm</code></li>
                            <li>Create: <code>lib/Comserv/Model/Schema/Ency/Result/DocumentationRoleAccess.pm</code></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Day 3:</strong> Write relationship mappings between Result classes
                        <ul>
                            <li>Add relationships in Result classes (has_many, belongs_to, many_to_many)</li>
                            <li>Test: <code>carton exec prove -lv t/model_AIChat.t</code></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Day 4:</strong> Create helper repository class for AI Chat queries
                        <ul>
                            <li>Create: <code>lib/Comserv/Util/AIChatRepository.pm</code></li>
                            <li>Methods: search_documentation(), search_code(), log_conversation(), get_role_access()</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Day 5:</strong> Document Phase 1 completion in AI_CHAT_DOCUMENTATION_FEATURE_SPEC.tt
                        <ul>
                            <li>Update version to 0.03</li>
                            <li>Mark Phase 1 as COMPLETE in status</li>
                            <li>Add Phase 2 start date</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <h5>🟠 NEXT 2-3 WEEKS (Phase 2): API Endpoints & Controller Integration</h5>
            <div style="background: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0; border-radius: 5px;">
                <p><strong>Weekly Milestones:</strong></p>
                <ul>
